stories.title: Gayle and Dillon outclass Bangladesh
stories.subTitle: Bangladesh v West Indies, Rose Bowl, Pool B
stories.summary: Another paltry crowd watched another one-sided encounter at the Rose Bowl as  West Indies, put in, overcame a lively pitch to score 269 for 3, and then skittled Bangladesh for 131 to coast home by 138 runs
